name: Fate/kaleid liner Prisma Illya
description:
LoRA model Trained on the anime Fate/kaleid liner Prisma Illya

This is a Style Lora so if you want to get the characters back use tags most associated with the characters to steer the model towards then

examples:

1girl,busty, long_hair, blonde_hair, red_eyes, brown_eyes, very_long_hair, hair_ribbon, drill_hair

would get luvia

1girl, smile, short_hair, open_mouth, blonde_hair, brown_eyes, hair_bun, double_bun,

would get Tatsuko

1girl, solo, long_hair, bangs, brown_hair, black_hair, brown_eyes,

would get Miyu

1girl, solo, long_hair, blonde_hair, red_eyes, white_hair, grey_hair

would get Illya

1girl,dark_skin,pink_hair

would get Kuro

and so on

if stuck on how to steer the characters inputting an example image into auto tagger will help.

This model was trained with labels constructed using smiling wolfs wd-v1-4-swinv2-tagger-v2 at .25 threshold. Tags outputted from that are likely to match the training data.

Suggested base model to use for the lora is 7th animeC
